## Install

```bash
# npm / pnpm / yarn
npm install @presentation-skill-pack/theme-{{name}}

# pip (Python renderer)
pip install presentation-skill-pack-theme-{{name}}
```

## Usage

Add the theme name to your deck JSON:

```json
{
  "type": "deck",
  "meta": {
    "title": "My Presentation",
    "theme": "{{name}}"
  },
  "slides": []
}
```

Then render:

```bash
presentation-skill-pack-render deck.json -o deck.html
```

